chelper.pl
v. 0.1

Simple perl plugin for the pidgin IM client to help with Chinese reading.
Can provide a hanyu pinyin "translation" of Chinese messages, as well as
converting between traditional and simplified characters.

To install:
1. Put chelper.pl into your pidgin plugin directory
2. Download/extract the CC-CEDICT dictionary file from
http://www.mdbg.net/chindict/chindict.php?page=cc-cedict and put cedict_ts.u8
into your pidgin plugin directory

If the plugin doesn't show up in the plugins dialog, https://developer.pidgin.im/wiki/Scripting%20and%20Plugins#HowdoIusePerlscriptswithPidginFinch

